So, Kumatora is aware that this is when Natsuki's insecurity will really start to boil over. Natsuki has been on edge all game, and while she's enjoying herself, anyone with eyes or a brain could tell she's really starting to feel bad about her body. That's why Kumatora is suddenly serious here. She's trying to give Natsuki some level of comfort. She wants Natsuki to know that both she and player find Natsuki to be genuinely attractive, but she doesn't want to overstep and hit on her when she's feeling insecure.
TLDR is that Kumatora is trying to show Natsuki that both herself and player are her friends and will accomodate her as she needs, even though she and player both find Natsuki to be hot.

This is the start of the interaction between Amy, Kumatora and Player. Whoever loses first has to talk about their fantasies about whoever wins, in the masturbation phase. For example, if Kumatora loses first, and then the player loses, then Kumatora will talk about how badly she wants to sit on Amy's face. The player is silent of course, so Kumatora could give dialogue to "steer" them through it, by describing what she'd want the player to do to Amy. For another example would be if Amy and Kumatora lose first. They both describe what they'd want to do with player, both one-on-one, and in a threesome. The "winner" gets rewarded by people telling them they're hot, basically.
